ro-label animate-blur-fade-up" style="--d:200ms">I build accessible, pixel-perfect experiences for the web.</p><p class="hero-anchor animate-blur-fade-up" style="--d:300ms"><strong>4.2k+</strong> GitHub stars<span class="hero-anchor-context"> — on Signal Forge</span></p><p class="hero-employers animate-blur-fade-up" style="--d:400ms">Previously at <span>Apple · Klaviyo</span></p><div class="pwb-hero-signals" aria-label="Availability and preferences"><p class="pwb-hero-signal pwb-hero-signal-place"><span class="pwb-hero-signal-value">London, UK</span></p></div><p class="hero-summary animate-blur-fade-up" style="--d:500ms">Jane builds accessible, pixel-perfect interfaces for large-scale products.</p><div class="hero-links animate-blur-fade-up" style="--d:600ms"><a href="mailto:jane@example.test" class="btn btn-primary">Let&#x27;s work together</a><a href="https://github.com/janedoe" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/janedoe" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="section-header scroll-reveal"><h2>Featured Projects</h2><p>A selection of projects I have built</p></div><div class="grid grid-3"><div class="card scroll-reveal"><h3 class="card-title"><a href="/projects/signal-forge/">Signal Forge</a></h3><p class="card-characterization" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#888;margin-top:-0.25rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">Open-source project · 4.2k stars · 23 contributors</p><p class="card-description">A tool for crafting proof-backed portfolios.</p><div class="badge-group"><span class="badge">TypeScript</span><span class="badge">Next.js</span><span class="badge">Drizzle</span></div><div class="card-footer"><div class="project-stat"><span>TypeScript</span></div><div style="display:flex;gap:1rem"><span class="project-stat">★ 4200</span><span class="project-stat">Ⓟ 312</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section testimonials-section"><div class="container"><div class="section-header"><h2>What collaborators say</h2></div><figure class="testimonial"><blockquote>“Working with her changed how we ship — the kind of engineer whose taste you feel in the product.”</blockquote><cite><strong><a href="https://example.test/alex" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Alex Example</a></strong> · VP Engineering · Acme</cite></figure></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="section-header scroll-reveal"><h2>Skills &amp; Technologies</h2><p>Technologies I work with regularly</p></div><div class="badge-group" style="justify-content:center"><span class="badge">TypeScript</span><span class="badge">Next.js</span></div><div class="text-center mt-4"><a href="/about/" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More About Me</a></div></div></section></div></main><footer class="footer"><div class="footer-inner"><p class="footer-text">© 2026 Jane Doe. All rights reserved.</p><ul class="footer-links"><li><a href="https://github.com/janedoe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li><li><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/janedoe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li></ul></div></footer></body></html>"
